    "40b70678-0961-4faa-a333-d639347a8503": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "402abe47-2834-405c-bf23-bec2557d4f25": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What payment options do you accept?",
            "content": "<p>1. Credit Card (Visa, Mastercard, Amex, Diners Club)</p><p>2. Wallets (<a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/pages/hairmnl-gcash-qr-code\" target=\"_blank\">GCash</a>, Maya)</p><p>3. 7Eleven</p><p>4. Online Banks (BDO, BPI, Metrobank, Chinabank, Landbank, RCBC, Robinsons Bank, UnionBank, UCPB, PSBank, Coins.ph)</p><p>6. Bank Deposit (BDO, BPI, Metrobank, AUB, Chinabank, EastWest, Landbank, PNB, RCBC, Robinsons Bank, Security Bank, UnionBank, UCPB)</p><p>7. Over the counter (Bayad Center, LBC, SM Dep/Smkt Counter, Robinsons Dep Store, Cebuana Lhuillier, M. Lhuiller, RuralNet Banks and Coops)</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--14240176472163__40b70678-0961-4faa-a333-d639347a8503-1676030332ea49b710-0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you accept COD payment?",
            "content": "<p>Cash on delivery (COD) is available only within Metro Manila and selected areas in Rizal. Delivery within 6 days. Cut off for orders is at 5PM daily.</p><p><em>Note: Failure to receive orders placed via COD will mean the customer will no longer be allowed to order via COD. Subsequent orders will be allowed only through other PAID options (credit card, bank deposit, 7Eleven, GCash, others).</em></p>"
          }
        },
        "b19aceb0-9ab3-4082-a92b-58e21b4150ac": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I pay through credit card?",
            "content": "<p>To pay via credit card, under Payment method: select 'Secure Payments via PayMongo.'</p>"
          }
        },
        "70c448de-d6d3-4a2b-aa0f-cc820bc3fb43": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I pay through GCash?",
            "content": "<p>To pay via GCash, under Payment method: select 'Secure Payments via PayMongo.'</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--14240176472163__40b70678-0961-4faa-a333-d639347a8503-1676030332ea49b710-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you accept payments by installments?",
            "content": "<p>Yes! Through <a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/blogs/news/installment-payments-now-available-at-hairmnl\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>BillEase</strong></a> and <a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/blogs/news/enjoy-your-hair-care-essentials-now-pay-later-with-0-interest\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Atome</strong></a> (0% Interest for 3 months using your Visa, Mastercard, Amex, Diners Club credit card)</p>"
          }
        },
        "3225ab47-99fe-486f-88c0-b130c07a9158": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is Atome?",
            "content": "<p>Please check out the link below to find out how to use Atome:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/blogs/news/enjoy-your-hair-care-essentials-now-pay-later-with-0-interest\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"HairMNL How to use Atome\">https://www.hairmnl.com/blogs/news/enjoy-your-hair-care-essentials-now-pay-later-with-0-interest</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "fd4c8cc5-50b0-41e1-a79b-aefae5445c63": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is BillEase?",
            "content": "<p>Please check out the link below to find out how to use BillEase:</p><p>https://billease.ph/blog/get-your-hair-care-products-from-hairmnl-and-pay-later-in-installment/</p>"
          }
